title: Pingfan Hu
text:
Hi! My name is Pingfan Hu. I am a PhD student and researcher at George Washington University in the Department of Engineering Management and Systems Engineering.
I have expertise in systems engineering and data analysis. I am working on projects of electric vehicles and renewable energies.
I mainly use RStudio and VS Code as working IDE, and I am experienced in R and Python coding.
